'''Sandy''' is the owner of [[Sandy's Sand Corp]]. His office is located in a small building north-west of the bar in [[Brimhaven]]. He owns all the [[sandbox]]es in ''RuneScape''. He is featured in [[The Hand in the Sand]], where it is revealed that he murdered a wizard and hid his dismembered body parts all over ''RuneScape''. Players discover this by slipping [[Truth serum]] into his drink. He disappears after The Hand in the Sand.

